description: After a new air fryer recipe? This tasty teriyaki salmon recipe is easy to make and ready in 20 minutes. Dinner's done in a dash!
name: Air-Fryer Salmon With Teriyaki Glaze Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Transfer rice to a bowl. Stir in two-thirds of the sesame seeds. Divide rice mixture and salad among bowls. Top with salmon and any cooking juices. Serve scattered with onion and remaining sesame seeds.
